nodes.text: Quadoro was a male Weequay pirate who worked with Hondo Ohnaka and Dok-Ondar during the Imperial Era to steal a relic from the Temple of the Kyber. The pirate was shot in the chest by a guardian after inquiring about why he had to walk at the front of the group.
Quadoro first appeared in Galaxy's Edge 3, a comic written by Ethan Sacks and illustrated by Will Sliney.
